Security Pacific Corp's SecurityPacific Merchant Bank said acting as lead manager it hasoffered 270 mln dlrs in 30-year and 35 mln dlrs in 15-yearmortgage pass-through certificates.    The offering is the second this year under an 800-mln-dlrshelf registration. The first was for 310 mln dlrs.    The mortgages were originated by Security Pacific inCalifornia.    The offering is co-managed by Kidder, Peabody and Co andShearson Lehman Brothers. Reuter&#3;